OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry although rather
OL,6,Fcloudy, some bright spells possible in
OL,7,Fthe south at times. Chance of the odd
OL,8,Flight shower across the north at times.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FThis evening will be mainly
OL,11,Fdry with the odd shower in the north.
OL,12,FThen rather cloudy overnight with a
OL,13,Flittle light and patchy rain in the
OL,14,Fnorth and east.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FA dry day on Thursday with
OL,17,Fsome bright or sunny spells developing
OL,18,Fby afternoon. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
